==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prerequisite
<hw>Pre*req"ui*site</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Previously
required; necessary as a preliminary to any proposed effect or end;
<as>as, <ex>prerequisite</ex> conditions of success</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prerequisite</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Prerequisite
<hw>Pre*req"ui*site</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Something previously
required, or necessary to an end or effect proposed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The necessary <qex>prerequisites</qex> of freedom.</q> <rj><qau>
Goldsmith.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Preresolve</ent>⟦br⟧
